init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look down and see a bee in a suit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm not a bee, I'm a human.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Yes, we know, but we think you're perfect for the job.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You just have to do one thing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have to make a wish and we will grant it."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I wish I could fly like a bee."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Your wish is granted." said the little bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You said you wanted to fly like a bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was stuck as a bee for the rest of my life.
